data.enText: to wrap sb/sth up or cover them or it completely

data.chText: 她裹在一条白色大毛巾里。
data.enText: She was enveloped in a huge white towel.

simple_means.memory_skill: en 使… + velop 盖上 → 把…包住，裹住

tr: enclose or enfold completely with or as if with a covering

value.def: If one thing envelops another, it covers or surrounds it completely.

example.ex: That lovely, rich fragrant smell of the forest enveloped us...
example.tran: 森林里那种馥郁芬芳的迷人气味围绕着我们。

partsOfSpeech.dec: de 去掉 + velop 盖上 → 发展
en 使… + velop 盖上 → 把…包住，裹住
re 重新 + develop 发展 → 再发展，再开发
